Class XPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tools.ant.ProjectComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class XPath
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task
    Ant task for performing XPath queries. Examples: 
      <xpath file="./plugin.xml" exp="/plugin/@version" prop="version">
    Extracts the value of the version attribute of plugin element of plugin.xml and assigns the value to the version property. If multiple xpath matches exist, the results are delimited by commas. 
      <xpath url="http://somehost/something.xml" exp="/plugin/@version" prop="version">
    Extracts the value of the version attribute of plugin element of plugin.xml and assigns the value to the version property. If multiple xpath matches exist, the results are delimited by commas.
